# BINARY SENSORS

#
# README file
#

# The automation with binary sensors ...
#  - is a fallback automation for the duration while the device is offline
#  - a binary template sensor per PIR is used to determine after the delay
#     whether the device was offline while the on_press event triggered
#     the fallback automation
#  - the main automation is with home assistant
#     - For details see
#       https://www.home-assistant.io/cookbook/turn_on_light_for_10_minutes_when_motion_detected/
#

